statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `news_categories` inner join `news_categories_pivot` on `news_categories`.`id` = `news_categories_pivot`.`news_category_id` inner join `news` on `news_categories_pivot`.`news_id` = `news`.`id` left join `reporters` on `reporters`.`id` = `news`.`reporter_id` left join `guests` on `guests`.`id` = `news`.`guest_id` where `news_categories`.`slug` = 'sports-9-18'

select `news`.`sub_title`, `news`.`slug` as `news_slug`, `news`.`title`, `news`.`short_description`, `news`.`description`, `news`.`publish_date`, `news_categories`.`slug` as `category_slug`, `news_categories`.`name` as `category`, IFNULL(reporters.name,guests.name) as author, IFNULL(news.reporter_id,news.guest_id) as author_type from `news_categories` inner join `news_categories_pivot` on `news_categories`.`id` = `news_categories_pivot`.`news_category_id` inner join `news` on `news_categories_pivot`.`news_id` = `news`.`id` left join `reporters` on `reporters`.`id` = `news`.`reporter_id` left join `guests` on `guests`.`id` = `news`.`guest_id` where `news_categories`.`slug` = 'sports-9-18' limit 10 offset 0
select `name`, `slug` from `news_categories` where `is_active` = 1 and `parent_id` is null and `in_header` = 1 order by `header_position` asc limit 10
